AUTOMATED ROOM
As you enter your room , the sensor sences your entry and starts a basic conversation and then according to your reply the further replies are given and then the main important thing that it can control your TV and also play music if your moods are bad and process accordingly .
It  also helps you to maintain your room temperature at a certain level according to your desire.
It initially measures your room Dimensions and then studies it everytime and learn the changes and then changes the temperature based on the required temperature and time of arrival.
At first , when you link your AC  with the maps and then when you start it sends signal or the AC itself reads from sensor , based on the distance and temperature depends on the usaage,
 
